events.name: Fifth Council's Annual Kayaking Trip
events.description: AK Chapter's annual outing! Come join us at the Numbai River for a day of fishing and kayaking! Lunch is provided, just bring shades, sunscreen, and a change of clothes.

events.name: South Chapter Fishing Trip
events.description: You know we're the best around when it comes to kayaking. We'll be trying spearfishing today, so bring your game face and tryhard mode.

events.name: Darth Maul's Friendly Boating Adventure
events.description: Attendance is mandatory. Soldiers who do not show up shall be executed.
